- Huh? Carol?
- Hi.

57
00:06:29,230 --> 00:06:32,570
Oh my G... What are you doing here?

58
00:06:33,070 --> 00:06:35,630
- Nice to see you! Hi.
- Hey!

59
00:06:35,660 --> 00:06:37,790
- How are you?
- Good, thanks.

60
00:06:37,840 --> 00:06:40,000
Paul and Carol Bates, this is my mother

61
00:06:40,010 --> 00:06:44,550
- and father, and, of course, you know Gail.
