62
00:06:44,560 --> 00:06:47,240
Well, you... you didn't mention
you were going to be here.

63
00:06:47,240 --> 00:06:48,440
No, it was sudden. Um...

64
00:06:48,470 --> 00:06:52,500
Paul got invited to lecture at
the Sorbone.(sic.) <i>Sorbonne.</i>

65
00:06:52,520 --> 00:06:55,170
Oh, how wonderful!

66
00:06:55,210 --> 00:06:58,420
Well, uh, Dad's here on business,
and we just decided to

