74
00:07:12,890 --> 00:07:15,590
But it's too...uh...
We're late...I think what we're...

75
00:07:15,660 --> 00:07:18,700
Tomorrow we're locked in
to a lunch at Brasserie Lipp.

76
00:07:18,720 --> 00:07:22,600
- Oh no, that's just...
