89
00:07:58,890 --> 00:08:00,240
He's brilliant.

90
00:08:00,510 --> 00:08:03,800
You know, I had such a crush on him
in college, and Carol's very bright.

91
00:08:03,820 --> 00:08:06,040
Well, he's a pseudo-intellectual.

92
00:08:06,050 --> 00:08:07,830
- Just a little bit.
- Uh, Gil,

93
00:08:07,830 --> 00:08:13,800
I hardly think he'd be lecturing at
the Sorbonne if he's a pseudo-intellectual.

94
00:08:13,920 --> 00:08:15,410
You should give him your book to read.

95
00:08:15,410 --> 00:08:16,990
Oh, come on. Why?

96
00:08:16,990 --> 00:08:19,050
No, because he could critique your writing,

97
00:08:19,050 --> 00:08:21,480
