181
00:12:11,880 --> 00:12:15,210
- Is that true?
- It would be in Moudon. He died of the flu,

182
00:12:15,210 --> 00:12:19,560
if I'm not mistaken. In 1917, I believe.

183
00:12:19,560 --> 00:12:22,320
- Very good, sir.
