1147
01:10:01,660 --> 01:10:03,660
- In the bathroom?
- Yeah. On the sink.

1148
01:10:05,100 --> 01:10:06,990
What the hell were they
doing in the bathroom?

1149
01:10:06,990 --> 01:10:09,050
I don't know.
They were just...

1150
01:10:09,870 --> 01:10:12,460
But maybe you dropped them, and

1151
01:10:12,830 --> 01:10:16,650
when you were putting them away,
and the housekeeper must've picked them up.

1152
01:10:16,650 --> 01:10:19,410
and placed them there, out in
the open where we could see them easily.

1153
01:10:19,410 --> 01:10:21,410
That was really thoughtful of her.

1154
01:10:21,410 --> 01:10:23,320
I didn't drop them.
I wouldn't drop them.

1155
01:10:23,320 --> 01:10:25,320
The important thing is
they're not stolen.

1156
01:10:52,630 --> 01:10:55,220
<i>C'est l'un de vos meilleurs, jusqu'au présent.</i>
