01:11:03,550 --> 01:11:05,920
I think 500 Francs is fair.

1161
01:11:06,100 --> 01:11:08,360
500 Francs for a Matisse?

1162
01:11:08,360 --> 01:11:10,150
Yeah, I think that sounds fair.

1163
01:11:10,150 --> 01:11:12,790
You know, I was wondering if
maybe I could pick up 6 or 7.

1164
01:11:12,790 --> 01:11:14,620
- What have we got here?
