1185
01:12:42,270 --> 01:12:44,440
Aren't you gonna get married?

1186
01:12:44,440 --> 01:12:47,320
Well, everything's a little
up in the air right now.

1187
01:12:47,320 --> 01:12:50,150
I don't know what is gonna happen.

1188
01:12:50,310 --> 01:12:53,610
Is there some place that we
can talk? Maybe more quiet?

1189
01:12:53,610 --> 01:12:56,280
- Sure.
- Come on.

1190
01:12:57,040 --> 01:12:58,690
Oh, Mr. Buñuel!

1191
01:12:58,690 --> 01:13:01,180
I had a nice idea
for a movie for you.

1192
01:13:01,180 --> 01:13:03,620
- Yes?
- A group of people attend a

1193
01:13:03,620 --> 01:13:09,200
