1194
01:13:09,650 --> 01:13:11,360
Why not?

1195
01:13:11,360 --> 01:13:14,820
They just can't seem to exit the door.

1196
01:13:15,470 --> 01:13:18,460
- B...But why?
- Well, <i>momento</i>,

1197
01:13:18,460 --> 01:13:21,640
when they're forced to stay together,
the veneer of civilization

1198
01:13:21,640 --> 01:13:25,380
quickly fades away,
and what you're left with is

1199
01:13:25,380 --> 01:13:28,470
who they really are:  animals.

1200
01:13:29,210 --> 01:13:30,260
