1201
01:13:30,260 --> 01:13:32,260
Why don't they just
walk out of the room?

1202
01:13:32,260 --> 01:13:33,770
All I'm saying is just think about.
Who knows?

1203
01:13:33,770 --> 01:13:37,440
Maybe when you're shaving one day,
