01:14:33,100 --> 01:14:35,400
I did feel,
for a minute there,

1208
01:14:35,400 --> 01:14:39,530
while I was doing it, like I was immortal.

1209
01:14:40,270 --> 01:14:42,090
But you look so sad.

1210
01:14:42,090 --> 01:14:45,440
Because life is too mysterious.

1211
01:14:45,440 --> 01:14:47,960
This is the time we live in.

1212
01:14:48,330 --> 01:14:50,920
Everything moves so fast.

1213
01:14:51,140 --> 01:14:54,890
Life is noisy and complicated.

1214
01:14:55,610 --> 01:14:58,590
I've always been a logical person.
I've never

1215
01:14:58,590 --> 01:15:00,240
I never acted too crazy.

1216
01:15:00,240 --> 01:15:03,740
I didn't stay here.
When I first came out here,

1217
01:15:03,740 --> 01:15:07,800
I didn't take a real shot at being a writer.

1218
01:15:07,800 --> 01:15:11,720
I'd just, kind of, be a hired Hollywood hand.

1219
01:15:12,370 --> 01:15:14,900
Don't laugh. I just want to...

1220
01:15:14,900 --> 01:15:18,020
I feel like I just want to let it go.

1221
01:15:18,580 --> 01:15:21,470
- Here.
- Oh!

1222
01:15:26,210 --> 01:15:29,690
Oh! This is...
This is remarkable!

1223
01:15:29,690 --> 01:15:32,120
Go on. Here, put in on.

1224
01:15:32,120 --> 01:15:34,120
They're so beautiful!

1225
01:15:41,010 --> 01:15:42,740
Look!

1226
01:15:47,430 --> 01:15:50,320
<i>Monsieur, Mademoiselle, on y va!</i>
(Sir, Miss, away we go!)

1227
01:15:50,320 --> 01:15:54,430
- <i>Qui est vous?</i> (Who are you?)
- <i>Allez monter. Nous allons trop tard.</i> (Come up. We're too late)

1228
01:15:55,080 --> 01:15:57,700
- <i>Allez!</i>
- Come on! Come on!

1229
01:16:14,900 --> 01:16:17,940
Oh, <i>mon Dieu</i>,
this is so beautiful!

1230
01:16:18,170 --> 01:16:21,720
It's unbelievable!
All the pictures I've seen...

1231
01:16:21,720 --> 01:16:23,720
Here it is: <i>La Belle Époque</i>!

1232
01:16:23,720 --> 01:16:27,350
Wow! I don't know
what it is about this city!

1233
01:16:27,350 --> 01:16:31,640
It's like, I've got to write a note
to the Chamber of Commerce.

1234
01:16:35,610 --> 01:16:37,570
<i>Bon soir!</i>
(Good evening!)

1235
01:16:38,260 --> 01:16:40,810
