(Good evening! Welcome.)

1236
01:16:40,810 --> 01:16:42,810
Thank you.

1237
01:16:42,960 --> 01:16:45,840
<i>Oh, mon Dieu! Quelle robe magnifique!</i>
(Oh, my God! What a magnificent dress!)

1238
01:16:45,840 --> 01:16:47,640
<i>Tellement avant-garde!</i>
(So ahead of the time!)

1239
01:16:49,320 --> 01:16:53,790
<i>S'il vous plaît, prenez un boire du champagne. C'est la fête!</i>
(Please, have a drink of champagne. It's a party!)

1240
01:16:54,670 --> 01:16:56,270
<i>Champagne.</i>

1241
01:17:24,690 --> 01:17:28,920
Isn't it amazing? The first time we met,
I told you about this place,

1242
01:17:29,120 --> 01:17:30,920
and the <i>Belle Époque,</i>

1243
01:17:31,170 --> 01:17:32,920
and here we are!

1244
01:17:32,920 --> 01:17:35,980
I don't know why,
but I have this feeling that...

1245
01:17:35,980 --> 01:17:37,980
I don't know, like I can't...

1246
01:17:38,630 --> 01:17:40,590
believe my luck.

1247
01:17:40,620 --> 01:17:44,410
Well, I can. I know exactly where I want to go next.

1248
01:17:44,410 --> 01:17:46,410
You lead the way.

1249
01:18:24,780 --> 01:18:26,210
Look!

1250
01:18:27,960 --> 01:18:29,960
