1254
01:18:36,670 --> 01:18:39,060
But, we know he's a lonely man.

1255
01:18:39,400 --> 01:18:43,180
- I'm sure he would love some company.
- OK, let's go.

1256
01:18:45,520 --> 01:18:46,900
Monsieur Lautrec?

1257
01:18:46,900 --> 01:18:50,180
- <i>Oui?</i> (Yes?)
