1258
01:18:50,220 --> 01:18:53,600
- <i>Merci, Madame.</i> (Thank you, Madame.)
- <i>Pouvons-nous vous offrir un verre?</i> (May we offer you a drink?)

1259
01:18:53,600 --> 01:18:57,310
<i>Je serais enchantée. Prenez un siège.</i>
(I would be delighted. Have a seat.)

1260
01:18:57,310 --> 01:18:59,310
He's asking us to sit down with him.

1261
01:18:59,310 --> 01:19:02,820
This much French I do
understand, and the gesture.

1262
01:19:02,820 --> 01:19:04,020
<i>Vous êtes Americain?</i>
(You are American?)

1263
01:19:04,020 --> 01:19:05,520
Yes, I'm an American.

1264
01:19:05,520 --> 01:19:08,850
<i>Je vous devine à l'accent.</i>(I could tell from the accent.)
- Yeah. Oui. Oui.

1265
01:19:08,850 --> 01:19:12,300
<i>Vos dessins! Votre attention! Nous admirons tout que vous faites.</i>
