1266
01:19:12,300 --> 01:19:14,760
- I love your drawings, also.
- <i>Bon soir!</i>
- Merci.

1267
01:19:17,370 --> 01:19:21,210
<i>Savez que moi je présenter Monsieur Gaugin</i>and <i>Monsieur Degas</i>.
(May I present Mr. Gaugin and Mr. Degas.)

1268
01:19:21,210 --> 01:19:24,070
- Bon soir.
- Enchantée.
- Bon soir. Enchantée.

1269
01:19:24,640 --> 01:19:28,790
- Paul Gaugin.
- Yes! Yes! Yes!

1270
01:19:28,790 --> 01:19:31,810
See the sketch he's made?
Nobody can draw like this today.

1271
01:19:31,810 --> 01:19:33,810
Not Picasso. Not Matisse.

1272
01:19:33,810 --> 01:19:36,180
Unbelievable. <i>Parlez-vous anglais</i>?

1273
01:19:36,180 --> 01:19:38,180
- <i>Non, monsieur.</i> (No, sir.)
