1349
01:23:29,850 --> 01:23:33,820
If I ever want to write
something worthwhile, I have to,

1350
01:23:33,820 --> 01:23:36,950
you know, get rid of my
illusions, and then I'd be

1351
01:23:36,950 --> 01:23:40,470
happier in the past,
as where I want a home.

1352
01:23:41,970 --> 01:23:43,410
So...

1353
01:23:44,060 --> 01:23:46,380
Goodbye, Gil?

